    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a museum-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the legendary S54 inline-six, retaining its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated dual-VANOS system. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension geometry is strictly OEM, preserving the telepathic steering rack feedback. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the bolsters are firm and the clear coat exhibits zero orange peel or swirling. A true collector\u2019s piece for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
