      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior finish remains in a flawless state with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin retains that fresh, new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases or wear, while the dashboard and trim remain pristine. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a full, documented service history from authorized dealerships, showcasing preventative maintenance that goes above and beyond factory recommendations. Every button, switch, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it were brand new. Includes two sets of keys, all original manuals, and a custom car cover.",
